args.title: Feedback: Excellent work and suggestion to keep expanding recommendations
args.comment_body:
First of all, thank you for the excellent work on this repository – it’s a fantastic curated list and clearly maintained with a lot of care and thought.

A few pieces of positive feedback:
- The selection is wide-ranging and includes both classics and more contemporary works.
- The categorization and structure make it easy to browse and discover new titles.
- The descriptions/notes are concise but insightful and helpful when deciding what to read next.

A small suggestion going forward:
- Please consider continuing to expand recommendations in underrepresented genres/regions (for example, more translated literature from Africa, Southeast Asia, and Latin America, as well as more niche genres like speculative fiction from non-Western authors). This would make an already great list even more globally representative and useful.

Again, amazing work – this is a very valuable resource for literature enthusiasts.
